reviewText: A real old Timmy porno movie!!!!!  Really funny wrapping it up in a Jayne movie.

Exploitative rubbish slapped together for a fast buck. The posthumous "Wild, Wild World of Jayne Mansfield" (1968) plays like a home-movie travelogue with lots of padding and astonishing bad taste   particularly the ghoulish final minutes. Actress Carolyn De Fonseca recorded Jayne's "narration." Cinematic grave-robbing at its ultimate worst.

The Wild Wild World Of Jayne Mansfield was released the following year after her death. A documentary of Jayne and her current husband Mickey Hargitay touring some bars and entertainment  areas of Europe. It is interesting to see Jayne in candid situations. Jayne fans love her in anything.
Good job , Its in good shape and it came very quickly. I will enjoy it for manny year to come.
